For Ahmed Ololade aka Asake Mr. Money, the 2022 Ileya festivities will be celebrated with fans. The ‘Sungba’ singer promised fans in a viral video that he would be performing live in concert at Sinatra, a lifestyle bar in the Adeniyi Jones area of Lagos State on Sunday, July 10. “I’ll be performing at the Sinatra Ileya special white party. Come outside and let’s do it the Mr. Money way,” Asake said in the video.   BBNaija to stream season 7 in the UK     Kanayo: Don’t pray to grow old in Nigeria     Joice Ize-Iyamu opens up on women’s contribution to…   Tagged ‘Asake Live Under the sky,’ the concert is billed to be an all-white Ileya-special party and an avenue to add fun to the long holidays. Music stars like K1, Pasuma, Peruzzi, Bella Shmurda, and many others have graced Sinatra’s stage and its adjoining club, Carica. In the last few months, Sinatra has been a hub for lovers of good music, quality entertainment, and a relaxing ambiance.